{"tid":1369003,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋求共識]聽日入元朗買老婆餅，最好幾點走？","createTime":"2019-07-26T15:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T09:11:11.000Z","uid":213656,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"95569374f3c267078f61c98e87d6f83836884a8d","tid":1369003,"uid":213656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:12:52.000Z","msg":"我諗大家對聽日元朗行動都有個基本概念，就係冇突發情況，例如冇人主動襲擊我哋/有人發神經主動挑圍村機，成場行動都係以和理優為核心，而且會入夜前走<br />\n<br />\n但我知每次行動都一定有人會留到最後，無論係唔想散得咁快又好，定留係現場食花生都好，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">總之一定唔會話走就走到哂</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n咁不如依家就有個基本共識，就係喺19:00左右，大家就開始準備返歸，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">喺20:00點前就散哂好唔好?唔好再守喺條大馬路度等俾人清場或者俾彈藥對面大造文章</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>另外，聽日若出現意外情況，此POST一切提議作廢</strong><br />\n正評：好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負評：唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd20f7294140cda6736dfd3bf133ed0871d159e5","tid":1369003,"uid":213656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9191dec83cb0c75dcd3b4bcfce3eb7b11e61bf53","tid":1369003,"uid":260695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:57:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc088736a836d8ef148ab404a309ba5fda327dc8","tid":1369003,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893711af55fc27fbf537256997b08e1fc1994693","tid":1369003,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"